commit.message: Added an onItemClickListener to the friend selection list. Now it needs to be set so it will actually send a friend request.
Added some hierarchy to the login and register pages as well as added the stubs for the activities required for viewing and adding friends.
Added a username to the userinformation. Each username may only be used by one user.
Made password fields hide password while it is being typed, added a password confirmation box on registration, and reformatted the way location is stored in the database.
Made communication between two devices work!
Added click listener to user list
FInished User List to display all the user names

Pushing updated working compass application w/o GPS support.
Compass image updated to arrow.
Android Manifest updated with GPS permissions.
